metadata.name: VLVT Pass
metadata.description:

VLVT Pass is an exclusive members club, comprising some of the most accomplished individuals from web3 and IRL, who are passionate about networking and providing real-world access to members which opens possibilities to the new business opportunities, exposure to new ideas, and the ability to build professional relationships with successful and influential people.

On top of all utilities, VLVT Pass provides you with free pfp collections, genesis, tokenomics and entry to the VLVT ecosystem.
